<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.8.9">
<l>nantā narakat taḻuntā vakaināḷum</l>
<l>entāy toṇṭarā ṉavarkkiṉ ṉaruḷceyvāy</l>
<l>cantō kātalai  vaṉētā maraikkaṇṇā</l>
<l>vantō vaṭiyēṟ karuḷā yuṉṉaruḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My father, you who bestows [with] sweet grace, to those</l>
<l rend="indent">who become your servants,</l>
<l>The way of not ever sinking into imperishable hell,</l>
<l>[You of the] Chandogya [Upaniṣad], master, lotus-eyed one,</l>
<l>Oh, grant your grace to me, your servant.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
